race.comment: COSMIC EAGLE (8) is back from a break and will be improved on two recent trial placings. Has shown glimpses of ability and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside. Can make the perfect return. EXTRAGLOW (6) couldn't pay her supporters on debut when giving a bold sight at Gosford, only to be collared on the line. Is sure to have come on from that and can go one better. BIVACCO (2) exceeded market expectation first-up when beaten a neck at Canberra. Better for that and looks up to the task. THREE WISHES (3) knuckled down strongly to get within a length of the winner in third last start over the 1000m at Nowra on debut. Is another likely improver that warrants plenty of respect.
